Title: ContractorTimesheet
Description: Beginner's guide for building simple Web Application using ASP.NET MVC technology.
HomeWiki:
ContractorTimesheet is a very simple Web Application demonstrating usage of following technologies and concepts
  • ASP.NET MVC 5
  • Single Page Application (SPA)
  • MVVM
  • Entity Framework (Code First From Database)
  • Data Model
  • Password Persistence
  • Knockout.js
  • KnockoutMVC (Kmvc)
  • Unobtrusive JavaScript
  • jQuery
    • jQuery Validation Plugin with custom Rules, Messages
    • jQuery Form Plugin
